    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the hotlines. i've seen them. but they don't pay the bills. they don't make the debt go away. every time i think i've found a way to fix it, something else breaks. it's just constant. it feels like no matter what i do, i'm just digging a deeper hole. it feels hopeless.",
